ttps://dev.indexologyblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Muni_Bond_Performance_Rieger.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"Muni_Bond_Performance_Rieger\" src=\"https://dev.indexologyblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Muni_Bond_Performance_Rieger-300x182.jpg\" width=\"367\" height=\"222\" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nComparing returns of municipal bonds to other asset classes:\n\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Index:   </span></b>                                                                <b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">YTD Returns:</span></b>\n\nS&amp;P 500 (TR)                                                          10.14%\n\nS&amp;P GSCI (TR)                                                         -0.19%\n\nS&amp;P National Municipal                                              0.11%\n\nS&amp;P Municipal High Yield                                           1.68%\n\nS&amp;P/BGCantor US Treasury 7 – 10 Yr                     -1.33%\n\nTaxable Equivalent Yield based on a 35% marginal tax rate','',23,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/?p=26',0,'revision','',0);
