loss of 12 basis points this month.  However, the sector is still positive 1.0% YTD and is the only one up in the index for the year. Supporting the S&amp;P GSCI Energy is the S&amp;P GSCI Natural Gas, which is up 6.2% this week, bringing the month’s return to 9.2% and YTD to 10.9%. Continued  larger-than-expected inventory drawdowns on cold weather and above-average nuclear power plant outages kept the momentum to the upside.\n\n&nbsp;','',43,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/?p=46',0,'revision','',0);
