smallest stock in the universe. It is much more likely to be invested in Apple. The monkeys presumably did not know this, and thus, in a particular way, behaved anything but randomly.','',89,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/04/09/89-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0);
