, a gold buying festival, next month.  Also, the wedding season has started and will continue until June. The DJ-UBS CI Silver Subindex hit its lowest level on April 19, 2013 since Oct 4, 2010.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>To sweeten the softs, the harvest of cane and output of sugar was slowed by a very rainy start to April.  Also, Brazil\'s coffee areas have moved northwards, so the frost may not affect the crop as much as in past years as the frost-risk period approaches. The DJ-UBS CI Coffee and Sugar are up 2.6%, and 1.3%, respectively MTD.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;','',276,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/05/09/276-revision/',0,'revision','',0);
