<li><b>Physiotherapy Associates</b> is in monetary default as a coupon payment has been missed.</li>\n	<li><b>Harrah’s Operating Company</b> bonds dropped as Ceasars Entertainment missed estimates due to revenue declines in their main markets.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;','',321,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/05/15/321-revision/',0,'revision','',0);
