py Associates</b> is in monetary default as a coupon payment has been missed.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Harrah’s Operating Company</b> bonds dropped as Ceasars Entertainment missed estimates due to revenue declines in their main markets.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-324\" alt=\"Bottom 10 Issues\" src=\"https://dev.indexologyblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/10-Down-600x225.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','',321,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/05/15/321-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
