om 1/6/78 - 6/18/12. Charts and graphs are provided for illustrative purposes only.  Indices are unmanaged statistical composites and their returns do not include payment of any sales charges or fees an investor would pay to purchase the securities the index represents.  Such costs would lower performance.  It is not possible to invest directly in an index.  Past performance is not an indication of future results. The inception date for the S&amp;P GSCI was May 1, 1991, at the market close.  All information presented prior to the index inception date is back-tested.  \" src=\"https://dev.indexologyblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/SPGSCI-Precious-Metals-600x436.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"436\" /></a><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\">Source: S&amp;P Dow Jones Indices. Daily data from 1/6/78 - 6/18/12. Charts and graphs are provided for illustrative purposes only. Indices are unmanaged statistical composites and their returns do not include payment of any sales charges or fees an investor would pay to purchase the securities the index represents. Such costs would lower performance. It is not possible to invest directly in an index. Past performance is not an indication of future results. The inception date for the S&amp;P GSCI was May 1, 1991, at the market close. All information presented prior to the index inception date is back-tested.</em></em></dd></dl>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','',550,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/06/18/550-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
