e\" target=\"_blank\">SPIVA </a>reports, which have demonstrated for years that most active managers underperform most of the time.  Passive management is not only a bargain -- more often than not, it\'s enhanced performance as well.','',797,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/07/03/797-revision/',0,'revision','',0);
