asury Index fell -1.61%, with its 7-10 year counterpart off -0.43%  Shorter duration indices dodged the bullet; the S&amp;P/LSTA U.S. Leveraged Loan 100 Index gained +1.22% in July.','',1001,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/08/02/1001-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
