gain and the negative average a 4.28% loss.\n\nAs always, investors are best served by not accepting the conventional wisdom at face value.\n\n&nbsp;','',1039,'https://dev.indexologyblog.com/2013/08/06/1039-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
